T02D2611:83a-1: a'a rya manydzu shr'i tsa rya marga bi dhi:/
T02D2611:83a-3: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi spyod lam gyi cho ga /'phags pa 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal 'o ;
T02D2611:83a-4: / zab pa'i don ldan bde gshegs chos nyid sku //

T02D2611:83a-6: rje btsun 'jam pa'i dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //

T02D2611:83a-27: dgug pa la sogs gsang sngags ni //

T02D2611:83a-32: stong pa nyid las aa de bskyed //

T02D2611:83b-15: gtor ma aa las rin chen 'bru lnga bcud //
